 (312250003), <a href="/web/20180712205151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0336660&amp;fLockTerm=Magnetic+resonance+imaging+unit">Magnetic resonance imaging unit</a>
 (90003000), <a href="/web/20180712205151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0153633&amp;fLockTerm=Malignant+neoplasm+of+brain">Malignant neoplasm of brain</a>
 (428061005), <a href="/web/20180712205151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0235653&amp;fLockTerm=Malignant+neoplasm+of+female+breast">Malignant neoplasm of female breast</a>
 (372064008), <a href="/web/20180712205151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0006118&amp;fLockTerm=Neoplasm+of+brain">Neoplasm of brain</a>
