 (126926005), <a href="/web/20180712205151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0069515&amp;fLockTerm=Oncogene+protein+HER-2%2fneu">Oncogene protein HER-2/neu</a>
 (44368005), <a href="/web/20180712205151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0524850&amp;fLockTerm=Operation+on+nervous+system">Operation on nervous system</a>
 (16545005), <a href="/web/20180712205151/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0030231&amp;fLockTerm=Palliative+care">Palliative care</a>
